9
0:00:27.360000 --> 0:00:28.360000
Come on up.

10
0:00:28.360000 --> 0:00:32.920000
Sylvia's here to talk to us today about WebVTT, which is one of the standards for time text,

11
0:00:32.920000 --> 0:00:35.400000
which is under consideration by the W3C.

12
0:00:35.400000 --> 0:00:36.480000
Thank you, Sylvia.

13
0:00:36.480000 --> 0:00:38.720000
